<script type="text/javascript">
    var Today = new Date();
    var ErrorMsg = "";
    $(document).ready(function () {
        
    });
    function CheckDate() {
        //檢驗日期        
        var DateFlag = true;
        var SelectedDay = new Date($("#MainContent_selectJourney1_hiddentbGoYYYYMM").val());
            if (SelectedDay < Today) {
                ErrorMsg ="Reservation for Award Upgrade can be made from 3-7 hours (depends on routes) to 360 days before departure.";                 
                DateFlag = false;
            }

            if ($("#MainContent_selectJourney1_hiddenTicketType").val() == "2") {
            var ReturnSelectedDay = new Date($("#MainContent_selectJourney1_hiddentbBackYYYYMM").val());
                if (SelectedDay > ReturnSelectedDay) {
                    ErrorMsg ="Your return date is on or before your departure date. Please adjust the dates and try again.";                
                    DateFlag = false;
                }
            }
        return DateFlag;
    }

    function CheckDataInfo() {
        var flag = false;
        //var AvailAbilityStatus = "0";//機位狀態
        var SegmentSum = 0;
        var OverSegment = false;
        //Step 1:先判斷啟程日是否小於或大於回程日(小於:往下做 大於:顯示lightbox錯誤訊息)
        if (!CheckDate()) {
            alert_fancybox(ErrorMsg, "", "MainContent_btn_Confirm");
            return false;
        }
        //Step 2:依不同功能做判斷
        $("#MainContent_selectJourney1_err").hide();
        $(".newcard-row input[type=radio]").each(function (index) {
            if ($(this).prop("checked")) {
                //判斷星盟來回有無超過6個航段數 By Winni Add 2016/09/22
                if ($("#MainContent_selectJourney1_hiddenFunctionName").val() == "staralliance-award-ticket") {                  
                    var BackSegmentCount = $(this).next().next().next().next().next().val();
                    if ($("#MainContent_selectJourney1_hiddenType").val() == "GO" && $("#MainContent_selectJourney1_hiddenTicketType").val()=="1") {
                        SegmentSum = parseInt(BackSegmentCount)
                        if (SegmentSum > 3) {
                            OverSegment = true;
                        }
                    } else if ($("#MainContent_selectJourney1_hiddenType").val() == "BACK") {
                        SegmentSum = parseInt($("#MainContent_hiddenGoSegmentCount").val()) + parseInt(BackSegmentCount)
                        if (SegmentSum > 6) {
                            OverSegment = true;
                        }
                    } 
                }
                flag = true;
                //AvailAbilityStatus = $(this).next().next().val();
            }
        });        

        if (OverSegment) {
            if ($("#MainContent_selectJourney1_hiddenType").val() == "BACK") {
                ErrorMsg = "Total segments must not exceed 6 per each ticket. Please try again."; 
                alert_fancybox(ErrorMsg, "", "MainContent_btn_Confirm");
            } else {
                $("#MainContent_selectJourney1_err").show();
                $("#MainContent_selectJourney1_pErr").hide();
                if ($("#MainContent_selectJourney1_hiddenTabName").val() == "Itinerary Change") {
                    $.fancybox.close();
                }
            }         
        } else {
            if (flag) {
                if ($("#MainContent_selectJourney1_hiddenFunctionName").val() == "staralliance-award-ticket" || $("#MainContent_selectJourney1_hiddenFunctionName").val() == "award-ticket") {
                    confirm_fancybox($("#MainContent_selectJourney1_hiddenConfirm").val(), function (resp) {
                        if (resp) {
                            __doPostBackLocal('btn_Confirm_Click', '');
                        }
                    }, "", "MainContent_btn_Confirm");
                } else {
                    __doPostBackLocal('btn_Confirm_Click', '');
                }
            } else {
                $("#MainContent_selectJourney1_err").show();
                $("#MainContent_selectJourney1_pOverSeg").hide();
            }
        }
        return false;
    }

    function CheckDataInfoConfirm() {
        var flag = false;
        var AvailAbilityStatus = "0";
        $("#MainContent_selectJourney1_err").hide();
        $(".newcard-row input[type=radio]").each(function (index) {
            if ($(this).prop("checked")) {
                flag = true;
                AvailAbilityStatus = $(this).next().next().val();
            }
        });
        if (flag) {
            if (AvailAbilityStatus == "0" || AvailAbilityStatus == "L" || AvailAbilityStatus == "R") {
                confirm_fancybox($("#MainContent_selectJourney1_hiddenConfirm").val(), function (resp) {
                    if (resp) {
                        __doPostBackLocal('btn_Confirm_Click', '');
                    }
                }, "", "MainContent_btn_Confirm");
            }
            else {
                __doPostBackLocal('btn_Confirm_Click', '');
            }
        } else {
            $("#MainContent_selectJourney1_err").show();
        }
        return false;
    }

    function RadioGroup(source, clientside_arguments) {
        $("#MainContent_selectJourney1_err").hide();
        $(".newcard-item input[type=radio]").prop("checked",false);
        source.checked = true;
    }    
</script>

<ul><li>Targets and methods: In addition to applying the collected personal information in ticket purchase, and any other pre-paid service, EVA Air will also use the information in the following areas:

The data will also serve as a basis for statistical surveys/analyses that will facilitate the provision of the services mentioned above.</li><li>For the presentation and marketing of products and advertisement, including the services and products of the Company and/or of a third-party contract partner, and the Company’s contractors, agencies, subsidiaries, associated companies, group and/or business partners.</li><li>The personal information you provide is processed via computerized instruments, with the required cross border data transmission to the Company and its contractors, agencies, subsidiaries, associated companies, group, immigration authorities of the arrival country and business partners, for the provision of products and services. The Company shall make every effort to ensure that its employees, agents, contractors, agencies, subsidiaries, associated companies, group and partner service providers observe and adhere to the terms of this Privacy Policy.</li><li>When you book or purchase peripheral services (e.g. car rental, local transportation, accommodation, or other related products) through the EVA AIR web-site, EVA AIR mobile web, the EVA Sky Shop web-site and the EVA Sky Shop App, as the process may be completed through a third-party transaction platform, hence the personal information and the finance-related information you input may be collected by suppliers of related travel products for subsequent service provision.</li></ul></li></ul><p >We promise that, without your consent, we will neither disclose your personal information to a third party irrelevant to the named service nor use it for any purpose other than that aforementioned, with the following exceptions: Your personal information may be disclosed, or used, in cooperation with legal investigations initiated by judicial authorities or authorities concerned as per duties and responsibilities.</p><h2 >Other important information</h2><div >FFP Member’s personal information may be disclosed to the Company’s co-branded card issuers.</div><ul ><li>Purpose: to inform FFP Members of marketing/promotional events and special offerings concerning the co-branded cards. </li><li>The personal information that may be disclosed includes: Chinese/English full name, gender, I.D. Card number, membership card number/type, year of birth, telephone number, mobile phone number and home address. </li><li>Usage period: within the period of existence of the contractual relationship between the Company and co-branded card issuers, the record retention period stipulated by relevant regulations, or according to the terms and conditions of the co-branded card issuers. </li><li>Targets and regions: the co-branded card issuers and locations of their contractors for handling related affairs. </li><li>Methods: the collection, processing, all kinds of international transmission and use of personal information in accordance with the regulations of the Personal Information Protection Act of Taiwan (such as digital files, paper documents, phone, or any other method considered fit for dominant technologies at the time of data collection)</li></ul><p >In accordance with Article L.237-7 of French Internal Security Code, please be informed that airlines may be required to communicate personal data to authorized booking, check-in and boarding data collected from their passengers (API/PNR) to the French authorities for the purposes and under conditions as defined in the Decret N° 2014-1095 dated 26/09/2014.</p><h2 >Passenger's rights to his/her personal information</h2><p >Anyone who voluntarily provides the Company with his/her personal information is entitled to the following rights according to the Article 3 of Taiwan Personal Information Protection Act and Article 16 to 20 of EU General Data Protection Regulation:</p><ul ><li>make an enquiry or request reviewing the information</li><li>request a copy of the information </li><li>request supplementation or corrections </li><li>request stopping of data collection, handling or utilization </li><li>request restriction of processing </li><li>request restriction of automated decision-making, including profiling </li><li>request deletion ( we may not process or answer your case or other service requests to the extent processing is necessary and the right to erasure shall not be applied according to applicable data protection laws.) </li><li>request of data portability</li></ul><p >You can exercise any of the aforementioned rights through our worldwide business offices; your request will be handled as soon as your identity is verified. To request the personal data removal, you will need to download the request form (<a xlink:href="tcm:35-55503" title="application-form-for-the-removal-of-personal-date-doc" target="_blank" xlink:title="application-form-for-the-removal-of-personal-date-en-doc" >Click on this link to download the Personal Data Removal Request Form</a>). After completing the request form, please submit the request form in person to our offices worldwide.</p><p >We will keep your information for as long as it is necessary to fulfill the purpose for which it was collected. For example, the legal or business purposes of EVA, or as required by relevant laws.</p><p >We will keep the information, so we can fulfil the specific travel arrangements you have made and after that, we will keep the information for a period which enables us to handle or respond to any complaints, queries or concerns relating to the travel agreement and the information may also be retained so that we can continue to improve your experience with us.</p><p >If you provide incorrect or incomplete personal information, such as a nickname, which prevents us from verifying your real identity, we might be unable to uphold your exercise of privacy rights listed above.</p><h2 >Collection of information through 'Cookies'</h2><p >A 'cookie' is a small piece of data sent by a web server to be stored on a web browser. The data collected from cookies is to differentiate the preference of the individual user. Most of the web-sites may use cookies to provide services to their customers. However, a cookie will only identify the use of the computer other than the user. Therefore, you can configure your browser to not accept cookies if you choose, however, if you disable your cookies, you will not have access to certain personalized features or participate in all of the activities on the web-sites.</p><p >Keeping our commitment:</p><p >EVA AIR will not disclose the data obtained from the Cookies in order to safeguard your privacy. Our email may contain electronic images known as Web Beacons that allow us to know whether and how many times, our email are opend and verify any click through to links within the email. The Web Beacons will be deleted when you delete the email.</p><h2 >Data profiling and automated decision-making</h2><p >Marketing activities of EVA AIR and its affiliates or service providers target specific information for users who make reservations through EVA AIR, including the total amount of the transaction and the system generated booking reference and travel itinerary, IP address, etc. We will use this information to observe the effectiveness of our marketing activities and may disclose this information to our partners for similar purposes. The third-party service provider organizes and reports on the collected information to provide better and more personalized transactions and various services.</p><ul ><li>To understand the habits of tourists, travelers, and members, as a reference for placing relevant marketing campaign information.</li><li>To unsubscribe the marketing/promotional message delivery, please visit the EVA AIR web-site to or contact EVA AIR local service center for more information. Link provided below:</li></ul><p style="margin-left: 40px;" ><a href="http://www.evaair.com/en-us/contact-us-and-help/contact-us/">http://www.evaair.com/en-us/contact-us-and-help/contact-us/</a></p><h2 >Self-Protection</h2><p >Please safeguard your personal information, additional services and all kinds of online services. Do not disclose your personal information to others. To prevent others from collecting and abusing your personal information, DO REMEMBER TO LOG OUT of the site when you complete a transaction (incl. Internet reservation, shopping, member contact or other data change), and close the window before you leave the site if you share a computer with others.</p><h2 >Modification of the Privacy & Security Statement </h2><p >EVA AIR reserves the right to change these guidelines and disclaimers from time to time, and the content presented on this page is considered to be the latest version. Should a material modification to our Privacy & Security statement occur, we will post those changes on our website so that you are aware of the changes. EVA AIR also regularly reviews privacy protection/security statements to comply with applicable laws and regulations.</p><h2 >Secure Website</h2><p >In order to protect yourself in the Cyber world, you should validate whether or not the website you're visiting is indeed a legitimate website.
